</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_275_r1l20">Lıeber valkenſteiner / Vns hat fürgelegt Alheid dıe Peter
            Prünſterin </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_275_r1l21">
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Burgerin . vvie daʒ ewr dıener Hans Murr <del rend="strikethrough">her cʒu Jr in Jr </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_275_r1l22">
<del rend="strikethrough">he </del> vor etlicher ʒeite her in Jr herberg kumen vnd
            etvvıelang darynn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_275_r1l23">krank gelegen ſeẏ / vnd alſo etvvıeuil bey Jr vercʒert hab /
            das Er Jr noch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_275_r1l24">ſchuldig bleibe / darcʒu als Er vvider hinab auſʒ
                <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> herberg cʒüge </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_275_r1l25">do hab ſıe Jm <expan>gelih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> j pett . j
            polſter . j . decklach ij leylach vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_275_r1l26"> ij <del rend="strikethrough">han </del> küſʒ <del rend="strikethrough"><expan>gelih<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> / dıe Er mit Jm hinab braht
            hab / vnd alſo ſey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_275_r1l27">derſelb Hans Murr darnach von tods wegen
                <expan>abgange<ex>n</ex></expan> Alſo habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_275_r1l28">Jr euch <expan>ſein<ex>er</ex></expan> habe die Er gelaſſen hab
            . vnd nemlich irs <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_275_r1l29">pettgevvants / daʒ ſie dem ewrn in freuntſchaft
                <expan>gelih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex>vvund<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_275_r1l30"><expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . daʒ Jr
                <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> Burgerin daſſelb
            Jr pettgewant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_275_r1l31">wıderſchicken . Vnd Jr auch Jr acʒgelt daʒ der
                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> ewr diener </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_275_r1l32">bey Jr <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒert</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> habt </del> hat . vnd Jr ſchuldig bleibt
                <expan>rıchte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_275_r1l33"><expan>becʒale<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet / Alſo daʒ ſie darümb
